<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>제30회 예혼전 | 충남예술고등학교</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Song+Myung&family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --ink:#171a22;         /* 먹, 밤하늘 배경 */
    --ink-soft:#262b37;    /* 보조 패널 */
    --paper:#f6f1e6;       /* 한지 */
    --moon:#ece6d8;        /* 달빛 텍스트 */
    --gold:#c8a24b;        /* 30주년 금 */
    --vermilion:#b8402f;   /* 단청 붉은빛 포인트 */
    --line: rgba(236,230,216,0.14);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  html,body{
    height:100%;
    background:var(--ink);
    color:var(--moon);
    font-family:"Noto Serif KR", serif;
    overflow:hidden;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;
  }
  body{
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 15%, rgba(200,162,75,0.06), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 80%, rgba(184,64,47,0.05), transparent 50%);
  }

  /* ---------- 가로 스와이프 트랙 ---------- */
  .viewport{
    position:relative;
    width:100vw;
    height:100dvh;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .track{
    display:flex;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    overflow-x:auto;
    overflow-y:hidden;
    scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;
    scrollbar-width:none;
  }
  .track::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none;}

  .slide{
    flex:0 0 100vw;
    width:100vw;
    height:100dvh;
    scroll-snap-align:start;
    scroll-snap-stop:always;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    padding: clamp(20px,6vw,56px);
    position:relative;
  }

  /* ---------- 공통 장식 : 붓선 디바이더 ---------- */
  .brush{
    width:min(46vw,180px);
    height:10px;
    margin:0 auto clamp(14px,4vh,26px);
    opacity:.85;
  }
  .brush path{ fill:var(--gold); }

  .eyebrow{
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:clamp(11px,3vw,13px);
    letter-spacing:.35em;
    color:var(--gold);
    text-transform:uppercase;
    margin-bottom:10px;
  }

  /* ---------- 표지 ---------- */
  .cover .badge{
    width:clamp(84px,22vw,120px);
    height:clamp(84px,22vw,120px);
    border:1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius:50%;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    flex-direction:column;
    margin-bottom:clamp(20px,4vh,32px);
    position:relative;
  }
  .badge::before,.badge::after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; inset:6px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:50%;
  }
  .badge b{
    font-family:"Song Myung",serif;
    font-size:clamp(28px,8vw,40px);
    color:var(--gold);
    line-height:1;
  }
  .badge span{
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:9px;
    letter-spacing:.2em;
    color:var(--moon);
    opacity:.7;
    margin-top:3px;
  }
  .cover h1{
    font-family:"Song Myung",serif;
    font-size:clamp(34px,9.5vw,58px);
    letter-spacing:.06em;
    text-align:center;
    line-height:1.35;
  }
  .cover h1 em{ color:var(--vermilion); font-style:normal; }
  .cover p{
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(13px,3.6vw,16px);
    color:var(--moon);
    opacity:.75;
    margin-top:clamp(14px,3vh,20px);
    text-align:center;
    letter-spacing:.04em;
  }
  .cover .sub{
    margin-top:clamp(28px,6vh,40px);
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:clamp(11px,3vw,12px);
    letter-spacing:.3em;
    opacity:.5;
  }

  /* ---------- 인사말 ---------- */
  .greet blockquote{
    font-family:"Song Myung",serif;
    font-size:clamp(19px,5.6vw,28px);
    line-height:1.9;
    text-align:center;
    max-width:640px;
    color:var(--paper);
  }
  .greet .who{
    margin-top:clamp(22px,5vh,32px);
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:clamp(12px,3.2vw,13px);
    letter-spacing:.15em;
    opacity:.6;
  }
  .edit-note{
    position:absolute;
    bottom:clamp(64px,10vh,84px);
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.05em;
    color:var(--gold);
    opacity:.55;
  }

  /* ---------- 전공 섹션 표지 ---------- */
  .section-title{
    text-align:center;
  }
  .section-title .kr{
    font-family:"Song Myung",serif;
    font-size:clamp(40px,13vw,84px);
    color:var(--paper);
    letter-spacing:.08em;
  }
  .section-title .en{
    margin-top:10px;
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:clamp(11px,3vw,13px);
    letter-spacing:.4em;
    color:var(--gold);
    text-transform:uppercase;
  }
  .section-title .count{
    margin-top:clamp(16px,4vh,26px);
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(12px,3.4vw,14px);
    color:var(--moon);
    opacity:.6;
  }

  /* ---------- 작품 카드 ---------- */
  .art-card{
    width:100%;
    max-width:420px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:center;
  }
  .art-frame{
    width:100%;
    aspect-ratio:4/5;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(236,230,216,0.05) 0 2px, transparent 2px 14px),
      var(--ink-soft);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:2px;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .art-frame span{
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:12px;
    letter-spacing:.1em;
    color:var(--moon);
    opacity:.45;
    line-height:1.7;
  }
  .art-frame::after{
    content:"";
    position:absolute; inset:10px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .art-meta{
    width:100%;
    margin-top:18px;
    padding-top:16px;
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:baseline;
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
  }
  .art-meta .name{
    font-family:"Song Myung",serif;
    font-size:clamp(17px,4.6vw,20px);
    color:var(--paper);
  }
  .art-meta .medium{
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.05em;
    color:var(--gold);
    opacity:.85;
  }
  .art-title{
    margin-top:6px;
    width:100%;
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--moon);
    opacity:.6;
    letter-spacing:.03em;
  }

  /* ---------- 마무리 ---------- */
  .closing h2{
    font-family:"Song Myung",serif;
    font-size:clamp(26px,7.5vw,40px);
    text-align:center;
    line-height:1.6;
  }
  .closing p{
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(12px,3.4vw,14px);
    opacity:.65;
    margin-top:16px;
    text-align:center;
    letter-spacing:.05em;
  }

  /* ---------- 진행 표시 (도트) ---------- */
  .progress{
    position:fixed;
    left:50%; bottom:clamp(16px,4vh,28px);
    transform:translateX(-50%);
    display:flex;
    gap:8px;
    z-index:10;
  }
  .dot{
    width:6px; height:6px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--line);
    border:none;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:background .25s, width .25s;
    padding:0;
  }
  .dot.active{
    background:var(--gold);
    width:20px;
    border-radius:4px;
  }

  /* ---------- 좌우 화살표 (넓은 화면) ---------- */
  .arrow{
    position:fixed;
    top:50%; transform:translateY(-50%);
    width:44px; height:44px;
    border-radius:50%;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    background:rgba(23,26,34,0.55);
    backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
    color:var(--moon);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    cursor:pointer;
    z-index:10;
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:18px;
    opacity:.8;
  }
  .arrow:hover{ border-color:var(--gold); color:var(--gold); }
  .arrow.prev{ left:clamp(10px,3vw,28px); }
  .arrow.next{ right:clamp(10px,3vw,28px); }
  @media (max-width:640px){
    .arrow{ display:none; } /* 모바일은 스와이프 전용 */
  }

  .counter{
    position:fixed;
    top:clamp(14px,3vh,22px); right:clamp(16px,4vw,26px);
    font-family:"Noto Sans KR",sans-serif;
    font-size:11px;
    letter-spacing:.15em;
    color:var(--moon);
    opacity:.5;
    z-index:10;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    .track{ scroll-behavior:auto; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="counter"><span id="cur">1</span> / <span id="total">11</span></div>

<div class="viewport">
  <div class="track" id="track">

    <!-- 1. 표지 -->
    <section class="slide cover">
      <div class="eyebrow">Chungnam Arts High School</div>
      <div class="badge"><b>30</b><span>ANNIVERSARY</span></div>
      <h1>제30회<br><em>예혼전</em></h1>
      <p>충남예술고등학교 미술과 2학년<br>한국화 · 디자인 · 서양화 · 조소</p>
      <div class="sub">한 학기, 네 개의 시선</div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. 인사말 -->
    <section class="slide greet">
      <div class="eyebrow">Opening</div>
      <blockquote>
        &lt;여기에 30주년을 담은 인사말 문구를 넣어주세요&gt;
      </blockquote>
      <div class="who">미술교육부장 방 성 훈</div>
      <div class="edit-note">✎ blockquote 안의 문구를 실제 인사말로 교체하세요</div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. 한국화 섹션 -->
    <section class="slide section-title">
      <svg class="brush" viewBox="0 0 180 10"><path d="M0 6 Q40 0 90 5 T180 4 L180 8 Q90 10 0 8 Z"/></svg>
      <div class="kr">한국화</div>
      <div class="en">Korean Painting</div>
      <div class="count">지도 · 박영선 선생님 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 전공생 10명</div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. 한국화 작품 예시 (이 슬라이드를 복사해 학생 수만큼 추가) -->
    <section class="slide">
      <div class="art-card">
        <div class="art-frame"><span>작품 이미지 삽입 위치<br>(권장 비율 4:5)</span></div>
        <div class="art-meta">
          <span class="name">학생명</span>
          <span class="medium">한국화</span>
        </div>
        <div class="art-title">작품명</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. 서양화 섹션 -->
    <section class="slide section-title">
      <svg class="brush" viewBox="0 0 180 10"><path d="M0 6 Q40 0 90 5 T180 4 L180 8 Q90 10 0 8 Z"/></svg>
      <div class="kr">서양화</div>
      <div class="en">Western Painting</div>
      <div class="count">지도 · 이병주 선생님 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 전공생 12명</div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. 서양화 작품 예시 -->
    <section class="slide">
      <div class="art-card">
        <div class="art-frame"><span>작품 이미지 삽입 위치<br>(권장 비율 4:5)</span></div>
        <div class="art-meta">
          <span class="name">학생명</span>
          <span class="medium">서양화</span>
        </div>
        <div class="art-title">작품명</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 7. 조소 섹션 -->
    <section class="slide section-title">
      <svg class="brush" viewBox="0 0 180 10"><path d="M0 6 Q40 0 90 5 T180 4 L180 8 Q90 10 0 8 Z"/></svg>
      <div class="kr">조소</div>
      <div class="en">Sculpture</div>
      <div class="count">지도 · 김도이 선생님 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 전공생 13명</div>
    </section>

    <!-- 8. 조소 작품 예시 -->
    <section class="slide">
      <div class="art-card">
        <div class="art-frame"><span>작품 이미지 삽입 위치<br>(권장 비율 4:5, 사진 촬영본)</span></div>
        <div class="art-meta">
          <span class="name">학생명</span>
          <span class="medium">조소</span>
        </div>
        <div class="art-title">작품명</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 9. 디자인 섹션 -->
    <section class="slide section-title">
      <svg class="brush" viewBox="0 0 180 10"><path d="M0 6 Q40 0 90 5 T180 4 L180 8 Q90 10 0 8 Z"/></svg>
      <div class="kr">디자인</div>
      <div class="en">Design</div>
      <div class="count">지도 · 임계은 선생님 &nbsp;/&nbsp; 전공생 17명</div>
    </section>

    <!-- 10. 디자인 작품 예시 -->
    <section class="slide">
      <div class="art-card">
        <div class="art-frame"><span>작품 이미지 삽입 위치<br>(권장 비율 4:5)</span></div>
        <div class="art-meta">
          <span class="name">학생명</span>
          <span class="medium">디자인</span>
        </div>
        <div class="art-title">작품명</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 11. 마무리 -->
    <section class="slide closing">
      <div class="eyebrow">Thanks to</div>
      <h2>서른 번째 봄,<br>예혼(藝魂)이 피어나다</h2>
      <p>제30회 예혼전에 함께해주신 모든 분께<br>감사드립니다.</p>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>

<button class="arrow prev" id="prevBtn" aria-label="이전">‹</button>
<button class="arrow next" id="nextBtn" aria-label="다음">›</button>
<div class="progress" id="dots"></div>

<script>
  const track = document.getElementById('track');
  const slides = Array.from(track.children);
  const dotsWrap = document.getElementById('dots');
  const curEl = document.getElementById('cur');
  const totalEl = document.getElementById('total');
  totalEl.textContent = slides.length;

  slides.forEach((_, i) => {
    const d = document.createElement('button');
    d.className = 'dot' + (i === 0 ? ' active' : '');
    d.setAttribute('aria-label', (i + 1) + '번째 화면으로 이동');
    d.addEventListener('click', () => scrollToSlide(i));
    dotsWrap.appendChild(d);
  });
  const dots = Array.from(dotsWrap.children);

  function scrollToSlide(i){
    i = Math.max(0, Math.min(slides.length - 1, i));
    track.scrollTo({ left: slides[i].offsetLeft, behavior: 'smooth' });
  }

  function currentIndex(){
    return Math.round(track.scrollLeft / track.clientWidth);
  }

  function updateActive(){
    const i = currentIndex();
    dots.forEach((d, idx) => d.classList.toggle('active', idx === i));
    curEl.textContent = i + 1;
  }

  let raf;
  track.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    cancelAnimationFrame(raf);
    raf = requestAnimationFrame(updateActive);
  }, { passive: true });

  document.getElementById('prevBtn').addEventListener('click', () => scrollToSlide(currentIndex() - 1));
  document.getElementById('nextBtn').addEventListener('click', () => scrollToSlide(currentIndex() + 1));

  window.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') scrollToSlide(currentIndex() + 1);
    if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft') scrollToSlide(currentIndex() - 1);
  });

  window.addEventListener('resize', () => scrollToSlide(currentIndex()));
</script>
</body>
</html>
